\mt1 Hebrews  
\ip Unknown if consultant checked.  
\c 12  
\p
\v 1-2 Kurrngalju purlpijalu marrngurrangulu parrjarnayinganyjurrinyi. Palajunjalu parnpina wirrilkunyijaninyi nganin-nganin nyarra jinu jinanganyjurrinyipa jurtuku jinaku, nyarra kurlujartinyjurrangu pukun karrpa-karrpa warlirnayinganyjurrinyi. Nganyjurrulu yajalkunyi Jiyijaji jalypalu, kurlkarri malkunyi palinyngarra ngarrakunyju. Palinyju walangkarranguja jipikartijakun Ngarrkanga yijalmartaku jinanganyjurrinyi yijalu. Marlkarri jarrinyaku nayilamu jinajalu kanka mungkanga kurntany yija yiji. Jiyijaji miranungarra palaku, paliny munu purlu jarrima, kurlkarri marnikinyi yarti Ngarrkalu pikaly yiji jilkuliny, nyarra kurntany puru yakarna. Kuwarri kajaninyi wangka yiji Ngarrkanga.   